snippet: Security forces fired on stone-throwing Sunni demonstrators in the northern city of Mosul on Friday, killing one and wounding five, according to Iraqi officials.
abstract: Iraqi security forces fire on Sunni antigovernment demonstrators in northern city Mosul, killing one and wounding five.
lead_paragraph: Security forces fired on stone-throwing Sunni demonstrators in the northern city of Mosul on Friday, killing one and wounding five, according to Iraqi officials.
